This version: 
	- Complete CRUD for Jinterface, connect with ErlConnection via ecc_java

To build this code, run the following command:

erlc -o ./ebin ./src/*.erl

To run the program, first start Erlang like this:

erl -pa ./ebin ~/Documents/Riak/riak-erlang-client/ebin/ ~/Documents/Riak/riak-erlang-client/deps/*/ebin -sname n1@localhost -setcookie secret

erl -pa ./ebin ~/Documents/Riak/riak-erlang-client/ebin/ ~/Documents/Riak/riak-erlang-client/deps/*/ebin -name n2 -setcookie ecc-ycsb

Then, run the following in the Erlang shell:

1> application:start(ecc).
ok

ecc:list_neighbor().


net_adm:ping('javaNode@wifi-student2-46.sri.ucl.ac.be').
